<h1 class="title">bbtautau: Why the had-had channel is best</h1>
<p>
There is more ttbar background in the lep-had, because you have W-&gt;lnu decays
</p>


<p>
ttbar: had had : 3/5**2 (1/9)**2 = 3/5**2 (1/9)**2 =  0.004
         lep had:  2  * 2*(1.2/9) * 3/5 *1./9 = 4.8 * (1/9)<sup>2</sup> = 4 x 3/5 x 1.2 x  1/9**2 = 0.036
</p>

<p>
bbtautau: had had : 3/5**2 = 0.36
                lep had:   2 * 0.8 * 2 * 0.2 = 0.8<sup>2</sup> = 0.64x
</p>



